    <item>
      <title>奥尔班威胁称，除非匈牙利资金到位，否则欧盟将否决预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/orban-threatens-eu-budget-veto-unless-hungary-funds-are-released</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班表示，除非匈牙利能够重新获得因法治和腐败问题而被冻结的欧盟资金，否则他将否决欧盟的下一份长期预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/orban-threatens-eu-budget-veto-unless-hungary-funds-are-released</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 08:21:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
